{"tid":259172,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"關焯照：炒Bitcoin係人性貪婪","createTime":"2017-05-26T16:22:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-29T04:06:59.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"57fd8c88ca482df7886d6c70129e7a3a26b6e90c","tid":259172,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T16:22:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170526/large/1495793309_757f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170526%2Flarge%2F1495793309_757f.jpg&h=1e1eaecd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n對虛擬貨幣近日被瘋狂炒作，經濟學家關焯照認為：「啲人貪婪，個市升得快，總知喺爆破之前，我賺到就得喇！」<br />\n<br />\n關焯照指Bitcoin是一個好假的市場，市場投機氣氛重，大家才瘋炒Bitcoin。他續指現階段買Bitcoin都是投機性質、風險又大及搏短暫，並非長線看好Bitcoin發展成為有交易能力的虛擬貨幣，Bitcoin亦沒有財富儲存能力。<br />\n<br />\n關焯照又指出虛擬貨幣的交易平台欠監管，「最擔心入面嘅Bitcoin全部走哂佬，即係被Hacked哂，咁點算，邊個賠呀? 所以，Bitcoin不會維持（sustain）得耐，除非政府介入監管。」<br />\n<br />\n若要Bitcoin成為一種貨幣，關焯照指需要有政府支持或中央銀行發行。另外，市場視Bitcoin作為商品也不太恰當。關焯照提到金、銀和銅等商品均擁有本身價值，但Bitcoin只屬虛擬貨幣，其價值是接觸不到，跟傳統金幣、銅或紙幣不同；紙幣是由政府確定的法定貨幣，Bitcoin仍不未取得政府法定地位。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b20e07995c0ca309cc113af5590b58efb534f7aa","tid":259172,"uid":53687,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T16:36:57.000Z","msg":"炒樓都係人性貪婪添"},{"pid":"3e4aa017f30b466bcf203146649877189875bba7","tid":259172,"uid":104820,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T16:39:05.000Z","msg":"荒唔係條撚樣心痛自己當初冇入貨咩<br />\n葡萄呀嘛，唔抵得呀嘛，明架喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n擺低粒膠先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a8b5326c26995928d85f6807afbfd90e278dc1b","tid":259172,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T00:24:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>荒唔係條撚樣心痛自己當初冇入貨咩<br />\n葡萄呀嘛，唔抵得呀嘛，明架喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n擺低粒膠先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n條撚樣D論點, 真係連基本concept都無"},{"pid":"42c35f3a7a1cacf3f96c0b3e6260898201690724","tid":259172,"uid":35418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T00:26:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>炒樓都係人性貪婪添</blockquote><br />\n炒bitcoin係人生貪婪係因為炒樓係天經地義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5f8642b8973f75f3cc99480febd1716cb3a913a","tid":259172,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T00:28:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>紙幣是由政府確定的法定貨幣，Bitcoin仍不未取得政府法定地位。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無知真係好可怕！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20170403/bkn-20170403211802607-0403_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20170403%2Fbkn-20170403211802607-0403_00842_001.html&d=LtIbkOcu3DY%2FoUE7XZdWtk%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=a6c766d6\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20170403/bkn-20170403211802607-0403_00842_001.html</a><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">獲日本政府認可　比特幣曾飆7%</span></strong><br />\n04月03日(一) 21:18<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20170403/photo/bkn-20170403211802607-0403_00842_001_01p.jpg?20170403213240\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20170403%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170403211802607-0403_00842_001_01p.jpg%3F20170403213240&h=c4d24a2b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n沉寂了一段時間的比特幣又癲過！據外國傳媒報道，日本政府上周五正式宣布，在4月1日起，比特幣成為認可的法定付款方法。消息公布後，比特幣隨即飆升，今日曾高見1,152美元，大升7.2%，現時仍飆5.2%，報1,130美元，惟與3月6日收市新高價1,277美元仍有距離。截至目前為止，比特幣自2017年至今仍累升逾19%。"},{"pid":"04866bef42c1f22173b0be45f237a7f36e92566b","tid":259172,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T00:29:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>炒樓都係人性貪婪添</blockquote><br />\n炒bitcoin係人生貪婪係因為炒樓係天經地義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n阿經濟學家話：「Bitcoin只屬虛擬貨幣，其價值是接觸不到，跟傳統金幣、銅或紙幣不同」<br />\n<br />\n對阿經濟學家黎講, 佢隻手掂得到既野先有價值嘛<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd2347d5cf455290c91161ea15bffe00e9080c9b","tid":259172,"uid":90863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T00:30:04.000Z","msg":"阿媽係女人"},{"pid":"f95366ff3284fdf23c0e31560e2e58c5e4fb107e","tid":259172,"uid":35418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T00:46:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>炒樓都係人性貪婪添</blockquote><br />\n炒bitcoin係人生貪婪係因為炒樓係天經地義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n阿經濟學家話：「Bitcoin只屬虛擬貨幣，其價值是接觸不到，跟傳統金幣、銅或紙幣不同」<br />\n<br />\n對阿經濟學家黎講, 佢隻手掂得到既野先有價值嘛<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n炒賣既野必需影響民生,咁炒賣先有價值<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以炒樓炒舖炒車位就好應該<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n炒bitcoin係貪婪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fff5ea30450ad181c33b16529cd74eea3257bf92","tid":259172,"uid":35418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T00:50:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>炒樓都係人性貪婪添</blockquote><br />\n炒bitcoin係人生貪婪係因為炒樓係天經地義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n阿經濟學家話：「Bitcoin只屬虛擬貨幣，其價值是接觸不到，跟傳統金幣、銅或紙幣不同」<br />\n<br />\n對阿經濟學家黎講, 佢隻手掂得到既野先有價值嘛<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n炒賣既野必需影響民生,咁炒賣先有價值<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以炒樓炒舖炒車位就好應該<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n炒bitcoin係貪婪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢段野可以改成咁<br />\n關焯照又指出買賣樓、舖、車位的交易平台欠監管，「最擔心香港發生地震，即係被震冧哂，咁點算，邊個賠呀? 所以，樓、舖、車位不會維持（sustain）得耐，除非政府介入監管。」"},{"pid":"447984981ba675120b9be177dd5d11140db60f92","tid":259172,"uid":40628,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T00:55:01.000Z","msg":"賺錢係人性貪婪 <br />\n<br />\n無賞返工先係常態"},{"pid":"933afe9f2cd9707c5c3a9bfae900528178861d53","tid":259172,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T00:58:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>關焯照提到金、銀和銅等商品均擁有本身價值，但Bitcoin只屬虛擬貨幣，其價值是接觸不到，跟傳統金幣、銅或紙幣不同</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n金、銀和銅本身點解擁有價值呢？<br />\n因為呢D物質本身係稀有、原子不能仿冒、近乎不能人為製造合成、數量有限<br />\n所以人類古代時用以所為交易媒介, 造成金幣、銀幣、銅幣 (相對易仿冒)<br />\n(你可以話金、銀和銅有工業用途, 但因工業用途交易金、銀和銅只佔總成交好少)<br />\n<br />\n金、銀和銅係因為本身既特質, 而有價值<br />\nbitcoin係比金、銀和銅更加無法仿冒及無法製造, 係更好既交易媒介"},{"pid":"d5dc35face05e9f582514f61d1c3659fb1cb2e64","tid":259172,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T00:59:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>若要Bitcoin成為一種貨幣，關焯照指需要有政府支持或中央銀行發行。另外，市場視Bitcoin作為商品也不太恰當。關焯照提到金、銀和銅等商品均擁有本身價值，但Bitcoin只屬虛擬貨幣，其價值是接觸不到，跟傳統金幣、銅或紙幣不同</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n金、銀、銅本身就係天然既存在,<br />\n又唔係政府製造出黎既<br />\n<br />\n金、銀、銅既價值駛撚政府endorse？<br />\n<br />\nON<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"082b77f79c62b897bcfb9f4e6b11a4c770212596","tid":259172,"uid":67302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T01:13:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>若要Bitcoin成為一種貨幣，關焯照指需要有政府支持或中央銀行發行。另外，市場視Bitcoin作為商品也不太恰當。關焯照提到金、銀和銅等商品均擁有本身價值，但Bitcoin只屬虛擬貨幣，其價值是接觸不到，跟傳統金幣、銅或紙幣不同</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n金、銀、銅本身就係天然既存在,<br />\n又唔係政府製造出黎既<br />\n<br />\n金、銀、銅既價值駛撚政府endorse？<br />\n<br />\nON<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\non9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢用金銀銅既原材料價格黎決定貨幣既價值呀？<br />\n一蚊美金硬幣(假設有)同一蚊港元硬幣可能金屬含量一樣<br />\n但價值都完全唔同啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96756c1005f6f196a89db38aeb65b451cc61d04f","tid":259172,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T01:23:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>荒唔係條撚樣心痛自己當初冇入貨咩<br />\n葡萄呀嘛，唔抵得呀嘛，明架喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n擺低粒膠先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n或者係出口術叫人沽<br />\n自己低價入貨<br />\n<br />\n如果SFC監管, 就可以拉得"},{"pid":"13b7ec76022777b5cbd9536b03cf82d511b58e86","tid":259172,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T01:25:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>「最擔心入面嘅Bitcoin全部走哂佬，即係被Hacked哂，咁點算，邊個賠呀?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢個真係好笑, 你可以用OFFLINE WALLET架嘛<br />\n<br />\n咁金、銀、銅又點？ 比人爆格咪一樣無左無晒<br />\n紙幣又點？火警咪又係燒左無晒<br />\n<br />\nON<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 到佢呢..."},{"pid":"c9482a0a162c0c06a3abf28c3f0f616d81040796","tid":259172,"uid":46933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T02:04:10.000Z","msg":"比特幣不可逆全球即時交易既特性就係佢既價值<br />\n一有走資潮、戰爭、黑市交易果時就有用<br />\n市場拎依d無實質數據既交易做炒作理由<br />\n所以特別好炒"},{"pid":"ebe3b0ca6f68b9e333a183fea615310c6a2a3313","tid":259172,"uid":49144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T02:10:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>「最擔心入面嘅Bitcoin全部走哂佬，即係被Hacked哂，咁點算，邊個賠呀?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢個真係好笑, 你可以用OFFLINE WALLET架嘛<br />\n<br />\n咁金、銀、銅又點？ 比人爆格咪一樣無左無晒<br />\n紙幣又點？火警咪又係燒左無晒<br />\n<br />\nON<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 到佢呢...</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /